  24 Nov 2006; Timothy Redaelli <drizzt@gentoo.org> bsdiff-4.3-r1.ebuild:
  Oops, i forgot to remove debugging echos.
  Thanks to David Morgan wrt BUG #156136.
  Fixed RDEPEND, thanks to jakub.

*bsdiff-4.3-r1 (21 Nov 2006)

  21 Nov 2006; Timothy Redaelli <drizzt@gentoo.org> metadata.xml,
  +bsdiff-4.3-r1.ebuild:
  Taken maintainership.
  Revision bump: added support for large files (>2**32);
  respect CFLAGS and LDFLAGS.

  09 Oct 2006; Timothy Redaelli <drizzt@gentoo.org> bsdiff-4.3.ebuild:
  Added ~x86-fbsd keyword.

  30 May 2006; Mike Doty <kingtaco@gentoo.org> -bsdiff-4.2.ebuild:
  Removing 4.2 per ferringb's request.  4.3 has the same keywords

*bsdiff-4.3 (17 Sep 2005)

  17 Sep 2005: Brian Harring <ferringb@gentoo.org>: +bsdiff-4.3.ebuild
  -bsdiff-4.1.ebuild.
  Version bump, something of a maintenance release it seems. 
  Changes between 4.2 and 4.3 come down to using libbz2 rather then piping to
  bzip2.

  24 Apr 2005; Michael Hanselmann <hansmi@gentoo.org> bsdiff-4.2.ebuild:
